What it does is it looks at the direction where you descend the

00:00:05.097 --> 00:00:09.213
most and then it takes a step in that direction.

00:00:09.214 --> 00:00:11.698
But in Mt. Everest, everything was nice and pretty

00:00:11.698 --> 00:00:14.379
since that was going to help us go down the mountain.

