But now, what if we try to do it here in this complicated mountain range.

00:00:18.960 --> 00:00:24.030
The Himalayans lowest point that we want to go is around here,

00:00:24.030 --> 00:00:26.160
but if we do gradient descent,

00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:27.960
we get all the way here.

