00:00:29.730 --> 00:00:32.158
we look around ourselves and there's no direction where

00:00:32.158 --> 00:00:35.240
we can descend more since we're at a local minimum.

00:00:35.240 --> 00:00:37.539
We're stuck. In here,

00:00:37.539 --> 00:00:40.243
